Just for your information, JP, bots don't have the capacity to become 
pregnant. Read this: http://bwtf.com/bw/tvshow/interviews/protoforms.html, it 
says somewhere there that all protoforms come from The Pit and The Matrix, 
meaning no births from the bots.

::Kluster::

Kluster shakes his head. "We're not here to leave. We were sent here to help 
the Maximals."

He turns serious. "Down to buisness," he says, turning to Phobia, "What's 
this info you wanted to share with us, and why is it worth risking being 
scrapped by both us and the predacons, when they find out you betrayed them?"
